<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/weibo/user/2831150640" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>深圳卫健委的微博 - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>i@diygod.me (DIYgod)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/crop.14.15.448.448.180/a8bfee30ly8h8w71x1lgbj20d50d5mxt.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1711293727&amp;ssig=mwlXMq7iBw</url><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:22:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>120</ttl><item><title>【[失望]#情绪障碍或会引发全身疼痛#】引发全身疼痛的原因有多种，其中之一即是纤维肌痛综合征。#如何避免纤维肌痛综合征#？[话筒]医生建议：①压力不要太大，注...</title><description>【&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[失望]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shiwang-b4bf17068f.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E6%88%96%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E6%88%96%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#情绪障碍或会引发全身疼痛#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;】引发全身疼痛的原因有多种，其中之一即是纤维肌痛综合征。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E8%82%8C%E7%97%9B%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BE%81%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E8%82%8C%E7%97%9B%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BE%81%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#如何避免纤维肌痛综合征#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;？&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[话筒]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;医生建议：①压力不要太大，注意提高免疫力；②多倾诉，必要时寻求专业医生的帮助；③科学锻炼，比如增加有氧锻炼等👇🏻（央视网）&lt;a href=&quot;http://t.cn/A6TL6Ka9&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;网页链接&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; </description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6vdIfiYL</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6vdIfiYL</guid><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:16:44 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>自来水里有氯味，还能喝吗？别慌，这是正常现象。[举手]一般来说，自来水厂都会使用液氯进行消毒。为了保持自来水的消毒效果，和输送过程中避免被微生物污染，管...</title><description>自来水里有氯味，还能喝吗？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;别慌，这是正常现象。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[举手]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fd/2022_raisehand_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;一般来说，自来水厂都会使用液氯进行消毒。为了保持自来水的消毒效果，和输送过程中避免被微生物污染，管网末梢自来水的余氯含量，必须要在0.05mg/L以上。所以，自来水带有氯味，属于正常现象。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;如果自来水煮沸之后还觉得有味儿，可以打开壶盖再沸腾3-5分钟，这样游离的氯，就会散发啦&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[开学季]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（中国疾控中心）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho22ssdlrhj20u01ulqb6.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho22srdf24j20v30u043c.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6ucmk3gm</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6ucmk3gm</guid><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 06:40:39 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>[单身狗]#医生提醒千万不要这样缓解压力# 医生建议，可以通过听音乐、练书法、运动等方式缓解压力，不建议通过破坏性的宣泄方式、吸烟、喝酒等缓解压力。如果情...</title><description>&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[单身狗]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#医生提醒千万不要这样缓解压力#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 医生建议，可以通过听音乐、练书法、运动等方式缓解压力，不建议通过破坏性的宣泄方式、吸烟、喝酒等缓解压力。如果情绪低落、兴趣减退持续两周以上，或情绪过度焦虑持续一个月以上，都应该及时就诊。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; （央视网）&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;卫就想问问，当觉得压力大时，你们都是怎么缓解的？&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[跪了]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[跪了]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[跪了]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://t.cn/A6TyUNsg&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;网页链接&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6svmm1j5</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6svmm1j5</guid><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 02:21:58 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>“土偏方”有多野？以毒攻毒、符咒香灰拌水冲服…… 真是不得不“服”[good] #这6种病无法根治别再信偏方了#👇🏻①糖尿病②高血压③哮喘④阿尔兹海默症⑤银...</title><description>“土偏方”有多野？以毒攻毒、符咒香灰拌水冲服……&amp;nbsp;真是不得不“服”&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[good]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_good-0c51afc69c.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%996%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%B9%E6%B2%BB%E5%88%AB%E5%86%8D%E4%BF%A1%E5%81%8F%E6%96%B9%E4%BA%86%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%996%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%B9%E6%B2%BB%E5%88%AB%E5%86%8D%E4%BF%A1%E5%81%8F%E6%96%B9%E4%BA%86%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#这6种病无法根治别再信偏方了#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;👇🏻&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;①糖尿病&lt;br&gt;②高血压&lt;br&gt;③哮喘&lt;br&gt;④阿尔兹海默症&lt;br&gt;⑤银屑病&lt;br&gt;⑥近视&lt;br&gt;⑦过敏性鼻炎&lt;br&gt;⑧口腔白斑病（科普中国）👉🏻 &lt;a href=&quot;https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLcCEVTtPRYY53fB8n2GPw&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;小心骗子！这8种病一旦得了就无法根治，轻信偏方可能致命&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;小卫提醒，有病要及时去正规医院就诊，千万不要随意使用“偏方”“秘方”，容易给身体造成巨大的伤害。长这么大，卫宝们试过老一辈的“祖传秘方”吗？评论区说出你的故事吧，顺便让大家避个雷&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho1trfixbej20qf0audhu.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6s9rlIrg</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6s9rlIrg</guid><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 01:27:58 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>【[举杠铃]#2个无氧动作练全身#】无氧运动不一定要去健身房撸铁，在家也能做[磕到了]：①蹲起火箭推：双脚与肩同宽站立，将重物放于胸前，先做蹲起，再挺胸将重...</title><description>【&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[举杠铃]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/bb/2022_Weightlifting_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%232%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%A0%E6%B0%A7%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BB%83%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%23&amp;amp;extparam=%232%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%A0%E6%B0%A7%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BB%83%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#2个无氧动作练全身#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;】无氧运动不一定要去健身房撸铁，在家也能做[磕到了]：①蹲起火箭推：双脚与肩同宽站立，将重物放于胸前，先做蹲起，再挺胸将重物向上推举，一组15-20次，每天3-5组；②箭步蹲划船：左腿箭步蹲，右侧划船，站起时大臂向后发力，一组10-15次，每天3-5组。为了健康，冲！&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[冲刺]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/ac/2022_Sprint_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（CCTV生活圈）&lt;a href=&quot;https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5011082901913654&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;CCTV生活圈的微博视频&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br clear=&quot;both&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;clear: both&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;video controls=&quot;controls&quot; poster=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hno41d3y4rj21hc0u0acz.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 100%&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/mwxDM3wXlx08ddX9gMPC01041200s9Ps0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=1711286527&amp;amp;ssig=2Y4Mpds6HY&amp;amp;KID=unistore,video&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/drOU3NB9lx08ddX8UmE001041200e2Wb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=1711286527&amp;amp;ssig=Ezquq3rkSk&amp;amp;KID=unistore,video&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/NrFlhioYlx08ddX8hmxG010412008Tuz0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=1711286527&amp;amp;ssig=dE250zcELH&amp;amp;KID=unistore,video&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;视频无法显示，请前往&lt;a href=&quot;https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5011082901913654&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;微博视频&lt;/a&gt;观看。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/video&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6lfQ3rLD</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6lfQ3rLD</guid><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 07:54:30 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>【国家出手了！预制菜明确不许添加防腐剂[心动超崽]】3月21日，市场监管总局联合教育部、国家卫生健康委等六个部门，印发了《关于加强预制菜食品安全监管 促进产...</title><description>【国家出手了！预制菜明确不许添加防腐剂&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[心动超崽]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/ae/2022_CHAO_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;】&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3月21日，市场监管总局联合教育部、国家卫生健康委等六个部门，印发了《关于加强预制菜食品安全监管 促进产业高质量发展的通知》，通知中明确表示，预制菜明确不许添加防腐剂！&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[馋嘴]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;另外，通知也明确了预制菜范围，对预制菜原辅料、预加工工艺等进行界定。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;咱就是说，搬砖人终于能放心干饭啦&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[干饭人]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;👉🏻 &lt;a href=&quot;https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/O_WWbiH4Z4xH4XDwWUfhVg&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;六部门发文！预制菜明确不许添加防腐剂！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫新鲜事儿#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（健康广东）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho0umvqw9tj20u00gc76a.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho0umvrzshj20hs0dfq3y.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6kc8subh</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6kc8subh</guid><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 05:12:37 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>[doge]#这些隔夜食物没毒# 大家害怕家怕吃隔夜食物，主要是害怕亚硝酸盐和细菌。亚硝酸盐在人体内容易产生致癌的亚硝胺，而剩菜中的细菌达到一定数量后，可能会...</title><description>&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E9%9A%94%E5%A4%9C%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%B2%A1%E6%AF%92%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E9%9A%94%E5%A4%9C%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%B2%A1%E6%AF%92%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#这些隔夜食物没毒#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 大家害怕家怕吃隔夜食物，主要是害怕亚硝酸盐和细菌。亚硝酸盐在人体内容易产生致癌的亚硝胺，而剩菜中的细菌达到一定数量后，可能会导致食物中毒&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[二哈]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;深圳疾控的实验数据显示：常温下放置了24小时的菜，都或多或少检测出了亚硝酸盐，其中，叶菜类亚硝酸盐含量最高，不建议隔夜吃。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;其次，隔夜水、隔夜茶等能喝！而隔夜泡发木耳、银耳、蘑菇才是真危险，常温下会产生米酵菌酸毒素，会让人昏迷甚至死亡，煮熟了也灭不掉。所以泡发干货最好别超4小时！&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[话筒]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;阿卫建议，搬砖人想把剩菜第二天带饭的话，注意以下4点👇🏻&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔹剩菜要密封冷藏保存；&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔹剩菜在食用前，要彻底加热，高温“杀杀菌”“消消毒”；&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔹绿叶类的蔬菜常温保存容易亚硝酸盐超标，最好现做现吃；&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔹蔬菜建议冷藏保存。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（深圳疾控、科学辟谣）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho0r2r3ws5j20q00nddj3.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6jo9i0hD</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6jo9i0hD</guid><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 03:09:29 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>不就是腹肌嘛，卫也有，一整块呢[单身狗] 想要瘦肚子，不仅要迈开腿，更要管住嘴，#4类食物越吃肚子越大#，千万别碰👇🏻🔵添加糖：添加糖升血糖的速度快，...</title><description>不就是腹肌嘛，卫也有，一整块呢&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[单身狗]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 想要瘦肚子，不仅要迈开腿，更要管住嘴，&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%234%E7%B1%BB%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%B6%8A%E5%90%83%E8%82%9A%E5%AD%90%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%234%E7%B1%BB%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%B6%8A%E5%90%83%E8%82%9A%E5%AD%90%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#4类食物越吃肚子越大#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;，千万别碰👇🏻&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔵添加糖：添加糖升血糖的速度快，部分血糖就会以脂肪的形式储存起来。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔵精制米面：有研究显示，吃升糖快的食物（比如白馒头、白米饭等）更容易堆积内脏脂肪。《中国居民膳食指南（2022）》推荐，主食的总摄入量中，建议添加 1/4-1/2 的全谷物。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔵饱和脂肪：研究显示，过多的饱和脂肪酸会增加内脏脂肪的堆积。富含饱和脂肪酸的食物主要包括动物油、椰子油、棕榈油等，以及配料里添加了氢化植物油、植脂末、植物奶油的零食。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔵酒精：喝酒不仅伤身，还可能会增加内脏脂肪，可能是因为酒精增加了皮质醇水平，导致内脏脂肪积累。《中国居民膳食指南（2022）》建议，每天酒精摄入不超过 15 克。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（科普中国）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho0pjaxx69j20p61wzgqa.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1ho0pjbuln7g20p00cw1l0.gif&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6j2wD0bt</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6j2wD0bt</guid><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 02:16:13 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>【[困]#脖子粗细会影响睡眠吗#】#打呼噜并不代表睡得香# ，也可能存在睡眠呼吸暂停的风险，BMI超过24或者颈围大于40厘米就要引起重视。预防睡眠呼吸暂停综合征牢...</title><description>【&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[困]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%84%96%E5%AD%90%E7%B2%97%E7%BB%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E5%90%97%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E8%84%96%E5%AD%90%E7%B2%97%E7%BB%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E5%90%97%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#脖子粗细会影响睡眠吗#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;】&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%89%93%E5%91%BC%E5%99%9C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%9D%A1%E5%BE%97%E9%A6%99%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E6%89%93%E5%91%BC%E5%99%9C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%9D%A1%E5%BE%97%E9%A6%99%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#打呼噜并不代表睡得香#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ，也可能存在睡眠呼吸暂停的风险，BMI超过24或者颈围大于40厘米就要引起重视。预防睡眠呼吸暂停综合征牢记这4点：①把体重控制在合理范围内，尤其是颌面部结构有异常的人群；②采取侧卧位睡姿，同时还要戒烟、戒酒；③有基础疾病的患者要积极治疗；④其他方法，比如做舌体操等。周五了，也别忘了早点睡&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[春游家族]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/2021_YoungFamily_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[月亮]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/w_yueliang-ec756dd13a.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;（央视网）&lt;a href=&quot;http://t.cn/A6TAyawG&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;网页链接&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6dFT9kIm</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6dFT9kIm</guid><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:36:42 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>近期，硫酸阿托品滴眼液终于获批上市了！民间传闻，阿托品滴眼液对孩子近视有奇效，真的假的[思考]？这种说法不严谨。[并不简单]阿托品只能用来延缓近视进展，不...</title><description>近期，硫酸阿托品滴眼液终于获批上市了！民间传闻，阿托品滴眼液对孩子近视有奇效，真的假的&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[思考]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;这种说法不严谨。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[并不简单]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;阿托品只能用来延缓近视进展，不能够预防近视，更不能治疗近视！&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[话筒]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;阿卫提醒各位家长，处方药有相对应的适应症和禁忌症，一定要经过眼科医生诊断评估开具处方后遵医嘱用药。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（科学辟谣）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnzxyfueh7j20rs0ku0wy.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnzxyebwrgj20u014tgpg.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6cNciy4z</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O6cNciy4z</guid><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:21:58 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item></channel></rss>